        <h2 class="section-title">Connection to the AEC industry</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          This article is relevant to the AEC industry because advanced AI could influence design
          decisions, structural analysis, cost modeling, scheduling, and project planning. If firms
          depend heavily on AI systems, questions about accuracy, responsibility, legal risk, and
          professional judgment become important.
        </p>
        <p class="section-text">
          It also connects to possible industry fragmentation. Different firms may use different AI
          platforms, which could create issues with standards, workflows, and compatibility. Larger
          companies with access to stronger AI systems may gain an advantage over smaller firms.
        </p>
